{"tid":798782,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解稱呼清朝皇帝一般習慣叫年號唔叫廟號","createTime":"2018-08-29T13:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-02T05:30:10.000Z","uid":100150,"like":13,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fbd997dd434ef0d5de6dede16a02add1514a7003","tid":798782,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"一般中學中史書都一樣，由明朝開始皇帝一生只有一個年，普遍叫明朝皇帝都習慣用廟號，例如明成祖、明神宗、明思忠咁，叫清朝皇帝就習慣叫康𤋮咸豐光緒唔叫清聖祖清文宗清德宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de7f5827b8d604aa7aa1c00b7948e20b00753fd2","tid":798782,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c0b3e5d296b5e5842d9f19b84abcef9cc8309110","tid":798782,"uid":23738,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"佢地個廟號好似好長⋯"},{"pid":"e37d23532a9e96f89f865f0129621ca2906a5ccb","tid":798782,"uid":11185,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"民國反清，唔叫滿狗做祖宗，於是叫年號，叫開就一路咁叫"},{"pid":"50aa45dd8c3bb1c439feede3d0aca884f7d61c0f","tid":798782,"uid":23738,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c0b3e5d296b5e5842d9f19b84abcef9cc8309110","tid":798782,"uid":23738,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:34:07.000Z","msg":"佢地個廟號好似好長⋯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"搞錯廟同諡號，自膠。"},{"pid":"ae7abcc444d2d5ffa4ab29c8a9368ad660274b7a","tid":798782,"uid":17427,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"因為清朝除咗太宗<br />\n全部得一個年號？<br />\n明朝都好似好多係稱呼年號<br />\n嘉靖 萬曆 崇禎 等等"},{"pid":"42d424e93319b041703fbaa1da982b26c3871df8","tid":798782,"uid":17427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ae7abcc444d2d5ffa4ab29c8a9368ad660274b7a","tid":798782,"uid":17427,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:41:48.000Z","msg":"因為清朝除咗太宗<br />\n全部得一個年號？<br />\n明朝都好似好多係稱呼年號<br />\n嘉靖 萬曆 崇禎 等等"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:43:06.000Z","msg":"自<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似冇答過你個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28917577d7e37e2db192f56789be19e524e8a186","tid":798782,"uid":42395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e37d23532a9e96f89f865f0129621ca2906a5ccb","tid":798782,"uid":11185,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"民國反清，唔叫滿狗做祖宗，於是叫年號，叫開就一路咁叫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"有D道理"},{"pid":"6590b33f7dfdea84a4571441f2714f5a2d4b10c7","tid":798782,"uid":192491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28917577d7e37e2db192f56789be19e524e8a186","tid":798782,"uid":42395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e37d23532a9e96f89f865f0129621ca2906a5ccb","tid":798782,"uid":11185,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:35:34.000Z","msg":"民國反清，唔叫滿狗做祖宗，於是叫年號，叫開就一路咁叫"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:45:57.000Z","msg":"有D道理"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T14:52:48.000Z","msg":"咁點解明朝都係？？萬曆帝 崇禎帝咁叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9181d00863744a19537173cb05267bcb1596f12","tid":798782,"uid":2467,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"fbd997dd434ef0d5de6dede16a02add1514a7003","tid":798782,"uid":100150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"一般中學中史書都一樣，由明朝開始皇帝一生只有一個年，普遍叫明朝皇帝都習慣用廟號，例如明成祖、明神宗、明思忠咁，叫清朝皇帝就習慣叫康𤋮咸豐光緒唔叫清聖祖清文宗清德宗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T15:10:07.000Z","msg":"傳統中史教科書寫清帝係廟號，如果用年號會加個帝字<br />\n<br />\n清帝的謚號太長，同埋會混亂學生。例考評局出卷唔會玩清仁宗清仁帝，前者康熙，後者雍正，即使用，都會有補充，否則玩死人。清朝有兩個皇帝係有兩個年號。<br />\n<br />\n通過個標準都係大眾認知程度。明清之前一帝多號，多數謚號或廟號算。"},{"